WEBVTT

00:00:58.867 --> 00:01:02.059
but continued to sleep on the floor
for several nights.

00:01:02.688 --> 00:01:07.265
It took over two weeks for her
to develop enough trust and confidence

00:01:07.940 --> 00:01:10.368
that this apartment was hers

00:01:10.392 --> 00:01:12.458
and would not be taken away from her

00:01:12.482 --> 00:01:14.696
before she would start
sleeping in the bed.

00:01:15.580 --> 00:01:18.338
Homelessness is a continuing
challenge for many cities

00:01:18.362 --> 00:01:19.694
throughout our country.

00:01:20.174 --> 00:01:23.780
Our homeless population falls
into three major categories:

00:01:23.804 --> 00:01:25.947
those that are temporarily homeless,

00:01:25.971 --> 00:01:27.698
about 75 percent;

00:01:27.722 --> 00:01:29.603
those that are episodically homeless,

00:01:29.627 --> 00:01:31.185
about 10 percent;